-- Russian steelmaker NLMK reports Q2 net profit of $158 mln
-- By Polina Devitt
-- Thu Aug 07, 2014 02:29AM EDT
-- None



MOSCOW, Aug 7 (Reuters) - NLMK <NLMK.MM>, one of Russia's largest steelmakers, posted on Thursday a second-quarter net profit of $158 million after $174 million in the first quarter and said it expected third-quarter financial results to be in line or marginally better.

